Version: 1.6.3.3
Revision: 1
Description: Emacs mode for Git
License: GPL
Maintainer: Sebastien Maret <bmaret@users.sourceforge.net>
Source: http://www.kernel.org/pub/software/scm/git/git-%v.tar.bz2
